=Generate 3 LinkedIn comment suggestions for this post.

POST BY: {{ $json.authorName }}
POST TYPE: {{ $json.postType }}

POST TEXT:
{{ $json.postText }}

EXISTING COMMENTS (for context, do not repeat these ideas):
{{ $json.commentsText }}

Requirements:
- Comment 1: Short (3-8 words), punchy and impactful
- Comment 2: Medium (2 sentences max), affirms the post's key point and adds a brief personal insight or observation
- Comment 3: Mid-length (2-4 sentences), different angle - could be personal experience, humor if appropriate, or a contrarian take

Return ONLY valid JSON with no other text:
{"comments": [{"text": "...", "type": "short"}, {"text": "...", "type": "mid"}, {"text": "...", "type": "mid"}]}

